         Description =+=+=+=
An override of the MEDI-SPAN indicator manually changing the coding
of the drug. If no override exists, this field will be blank. Example an N
drug, based on a Client?s plan setup could be overridden with Y code.
Valid values are:
*blank
M Multi-Source Not Generic
N Single-Source Not Generic
O Original, Generics Available
X Price as N Report as Y
Y Generic
Z O/R Gen Ind; Price as N
